  "texts": [
    "All the data analysis was performed with R (version 4.1.2), Graphpad Prism 8 and Microsoft Excel.",
    "The 2D areas of the organoids were measured with ImageJ (NIH) and the comparison was carried out with two-way ANOVA by normalizing the size of the organoids to match the average size of each group measured on day 5.",
    "For cell number quantification, positive cells were manually counted using the cell counter function in ImageJ.",
    "Group comparisons of Kaplan-Meier survival analysis of xenografted mice and mice treatment were calculated with Log-rank test.",
    "Students' t-tests were applied when comparing variables between two groups (paired t-test for drug treatment and heteroskedastic for the rest)."
  ],
